 REQUIREMENTS
 ------------
 
 - Java 1.5+ ( http://sun.java.org/ )
 - Groovy 1.8+ ( http://groovy.codehaus.org/ )
 - Parallel Kingdom account in the kingdom to be scraped.
 - Amazon S3 account ( http://aws.amazon.com/s3/ )
 
 INSTALLATION
 ------------
 
 [Amazon S3 Installation]
 
 1. Unzip PKBricks to a location of your choice.
 2. In src directory copy DEFAULT-config.json to config.json and edit it.
 3. Upload the following to your Amazon S3 account:
 	ajax-loader.gif
 	brickStatusDefaults.json
 	index.html
 	jquery.ba-bbq.min.js
 	pkBricks.css
 	pkBricks.js
 4. Run the PKBricks.sh script to run the scrape
 5. (Optional) Set up a cron entry to automatically update at a regular interval of your choice.
 
